u\u017e\u00edv\u00e1me platformu ESP8266, resp. NodeMCU.</p>\n<p>Na tento kurz je pot\u0159eba obstarat speci\u00e1ln\u00ed za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed.\nV \u010cesku se d\u00e1 sehnat relativn\u011b rychle, spolehliv\u011b a draze\nnap\u0159.\u00a0u\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.gme.cz/\">GM Electronic</a>,\n<a href=\"https://rpishop.cz//\">RPishop.cz</a> nebo\n<a href=\"https://dratek.cz/\">Dr\u00e1tek.cz</a>;\nv\u00a0\u010c\u00edn\u011b levn\u011b ale s dlouhou dobou dod\u00e1n\u00ed\nnap\u0159.\u00a0z\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.aliexpress.com/\">AliExpress</a>.</p>\n<p>Kurz je psan\u00fd pro za\u010d\u00e1te\u010dn\u00edky, ale pot\u0159ebuje hlavn\u011b ze za\u010d\u00e1tku\nrelativn\u011b slo\u017eit\u00e9 nastaven\u00ed.\nDoporu\u010dujeme proto za\u010d\u00edt s\u00a0n\u011bk\u00fdm zku\u0161en\u011bj\u0161\u00edm \u2013 nap\u0159. na workshopu\nnebo <a href=\"https://pyvo.cz/\">na srazu</a>.</p>","sessions":[{"materials":[{"lesson_slug":"micropython/flashing","title":"Flashov\u00e1n\u00ed (pro organiz\u00e1tory/kou\u010de)","type":"lesson","url":"/2023/brno-micropython/micropython/flashing/"}],"pages":{"back":{"content":"","url":"https://naucse.python.cz/2023/brno-micropython/sessions/setup/back/"},"front":{"content":"","url":"https://naucse.python.cz/2023/brno-micropython/sessions/setup/"}},"serial":"-1","slug":"setup","source_file":"course.yml","title":"Nastaven\u00ed za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed","url":"https://naucse.python.cz/2023/brno-micropython/sessions/setup/"},{"date":"2023-03-04","materials":[{"lesson_slug":"micropython/install","title":"Instalace","type":"lesson","url":"/2023/brno-micropython/micropython/install/"},{"lesson_slug":"micropython/micropython","title":"MicroPython na mal\u00e9m za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed","type":"lesson","url":"/2023/brno-micropython/micropython/micropython/"},{"lesson_slug":"micropython/intro","title":"MicroPython \u2013 taky Python","type":"lesson","url":"/2023/brno-micropython/micropython/intro/"},{"lesson_slug":"micropython/inp